  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406110/extras/977c455cf08c7a4ec018e4eb952b144e.avif?t=1614465415\" width=616 height=124 /></span><br><br>You need a job, so what do you do? Obviously, you start working as a demon hunter!<br>Explore the city of Nova Odessa and kill lots of demons!<br><br><br>Nova Odessa is a action/adventure game where you play as a novice demon hunter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406110/extras/2a36ee0b0fc1575a7aa7a8be99746d7c.avif?t=1614465415\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast-paced combat!<br></li><li> Find new equipment and upgrades!<br></li><li> 8 different areas with unique bosses!<br></li><li> Customize your home!<br></li><li> Become financially independent!</li></ul>",
